<br>
&quot;PoP flags: PoP was specifically designed so that only high-end guilds could get into the higher tiers. There will be no alternate means of entry to elemental planes, such as through quests. There's a second reason too. The loot in elemental planes is so good it's considered the reward for getting there. ie instead of putting good loot on Rallos Zek as a reward for killing him, they put good loot in the elemental planes as a reward for killing Rallos Zek. They'd have to tune it down if there were other means of getting into those planes.&quot;<br>
<br>
This is apparently SOE's response at a panel discussion.<br>
